# OLIV Phase 0 benchmark manifest — one JSON object per line.
# Copy to manifest.jsonl, record each clip (16kHz mono WAV recommended) into ./clips/,
# and set "reference" to the exact ground-truth transcript.
# Fields: id, path, bucket, reference, keywords (optional; used for KW-recall on
#         proper_nouns/technical buckets). Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
